OL,3,CJersey to update 20th Century abortion
OL,4,Clegislation
OL,6,FJersey government has announced it
OL,7,Fwill resume work to update the
OL,8,Fisland's 27-year-old abortion laws
OL,9,Fafter it was halted in the summer due
OL,10,Fto a lack of resources.
OL,12,FIt follows criticism of the Chief
OL,13,FMinister's comments at a scrutiny
OL,14,Fpanel on Friday 20 September when he
OL,15,Fwas asked why progress has stopped on
OL,16,Fdeveloping abortion law as well as
OL,17,Fother projects.
