OL,6,FDeputy Lyndon Farnham said: "We're
OL,7,Ftrying to find the balance that
OL,8,Faddresses the basics and we get those
OL,9,Fright first before we start putting on
OL,10,Fall the 'nice-to-haves' things."
OL,12,FThe comment concerned many including
OL,13,FJo Nash, founder of baby loss charity
OL,14,FPhilip's Footprints, who says: "I
OL,15,Fthink women's health issues are not a
OL,16,F'nice-to-have' - they are essential.
OL,18,F"I think it's really important that
OL,19,Fall of these things are considered -
OL,20,Fpeople's access to abortion should be
OL,21,Feasy and it should be free."
