OL,6,FITV News approached the Chief Minister
OL,7,Ffor comment, however, Deputy Farnham
OL,8,Fis currently away and was instead
OL,9,Foffered an interview with Deputy Tom
OL,10,FBinet.
OL,12,FTalking to ITV on Tuesday 24
OL,13,FSeptember, Deputy Tom Binet said the
OL,14,Fdecision to halt work didn't sit well
OL,15,Fwith him and confirmed that the
OL,16,Fgovernment has now found someone to
OL,17,Fwork up and submit policy documents to
OL,18,Fthe law department.
