OL,6,FIn response, Chair of the Health and
OL,7,FSocial Security Panel, Deputy Louise
OL,8,FDoublet, said: "Five days ago the
OL,9,Fpanel were told it wasn't possible to
OL,10,Fcarry out the work.
OL,12,F"We will be asking the Minister for
OL,13,Fevidence if this is indeed now
OL,14,Fpossible. The panel is minded to lodge
OL,15,Fan amendment to ensure that the work
OL,16,Fdoes definitely continue."
