OL,6,FITV News wasn't told what specific
OL,7,Fchanges the new laws would make, but
OL,8,FDeputy Tom Binet said that work is
OL,9,Fprogressing and that there would be
OL,10,Ffewer barriers to women.
OL,12,FCurrent legislation won't allow a
OL,13,Fwoman to terminate her pregnancy after
OL,14,F12 weeks under most circumstances, a
OL,15,Fshorter period than Guernsey and the
OL,16,FUK which sits at 24 weeks.
