OL,4,Clegislation
OL,6,FJersey women who want to terminate
OL,7,Ftheir pregnancy also have to pay for
OL,8,Fthe procedure.JIn 2023, Jersey's
OL,9,Fgovernment launched a public
OL,10,Fconsultation on women's experiences of
OL,11,Fabortion on the island.
OL,13,FOne respondent said: "There was no
OL,14,Femotional support afterwards. I went
OL,15,Fback to work the next day and cried in
OL,16,Fthe toilet."
