OL,6,FAnother explained: "The doctor I saw
OL,7,Fin the hospital didn't sign me off
OL,8,Fwork afterwards, so I returned to work
OL,9,Fless than 18 hours after waking from
OL,10,Fgeneral anaesthetic, still bleeding."
OL,12,FITV News spoke to one of the women who
OL,13,Fshared their experience of termination
OL,14,Fin the consultation regarding the
OL,15,FChief Minister's comments.
OL,17,FShe said: "The comment 'nice to have'
OL,18,Fmakes crucial women's care sound like
OL,19,Fan optional requirement and I'm
OL,20,Fdisappointed to hear that this is the
OL,21,FChief Minister's View.
